opengroupware.org (1.0beta.1-0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Bump OGO SONAME version to 5.2, ZideStore SONAME version to 1.4.
  * Add existing packages alternatives to each virtual build dependency.
  * Use libsope-dev as build-dependency instead of all individual SOPE devel
    packages.
  * Don't build packages with removed translations.
  * Drop Build-Dependency on objc-compiler. Always require gobjc. 

 -- Sebastian Ley <ley@debian.org>  Fri, 13 Jan 2006 14:11:02 +0100

opengroupware.org (1.0a.13-0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * debian/ogo-create-instance: Add a Default for skyaptnotify logging.
  * Added README.Debian for skyaptnotify, informing the user about the need to
    set up a crontab entry
  * Rename some toolname from sky* to ogo-*
  * Install new README.Instances which explains how to create
    OpenGroupware.org instances

 -- Sebastian Ley <ley@debian.org>  Sat,  4 Jun 2005 19:26:16 +0200

